src:
Jessi drops MV for 'Drip' feat. Jay Park
01 Nov 2019, 09:05 by germainej
Jessi has dropped her music video for "Drip" featuring Jay Park.The two rappers have come together for the fresh collaboration track composed by Jessi, johnjohn, and CuzD and written by Jessi, Jay Park, and johnjohn. "Drip" is also the second release after Jessi signed with P-Nation early this year.Watch Jessi's "Drip" MV above, and let us know what you think in the comments below.
